		- gnome.asia		(cert: guzheng.lyrical.net; shows empty tree)
		- 2012.gnome.asia	(ditto)
		- www.gnome.asia	(ditto)

		- gnomejournal.org		(cert: www.gnome.org; shows rt.gnome.org's data)

		- gnome.org subdomains:

			- admin		(shows blank page, mismatched, CN: www)
			- api *
			- art **
			- download *
			- ftp
			- jabber **
			- people **
			- projects **
			- webstats *
			- webapps *
			- www-old **

	* Prints "OOPS...", mismatched, CN: blogs.gnome.org
	** record_too_long


	Problematic domains:

		- foundation.gnome.org	(works, mismatched, CN: www)
		- label.gnome.org *
		- ldap.gnome.org *
		- usability.gnome.org	(prints "OOPS...", mismatched, CN: blogs.gnome.org)
		- (www.)gupnp.org	(mismatch, CN: www.webstreams.de)

	* Reply with http, redirect to live.gnome.org


	Fully covered domains:

		- gnome.org subdomains:

			- (www.)
			- blogs
			- bugzilla
			- developer
			- extensions
			- foundation
			- git
			- help
			- label
			- ldap
			- l10n
			- library
			- mail
			- mango
			- menubar
			- nagios
			- news
			- live
			- ostree
			- planet
			- rt
			- usability
			- vote

		- (www.)gupnp.org

